Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.10,0:01:49.65,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛が愛を「重過ぎる」って理解を拒み
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.82,0:01:54.45,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憎しみに　変わって行く前に…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.59,0:01:56.42,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何もかもそうだろ？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.54,0:02:01.44,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,バツの悪い事情にはいつも蓋して
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.55,0:02:04.27,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,食わせ物のリアル
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.38,0:02:06.60,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歪んだジレンマ時代で
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.75,0:02:10.36,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約束したはずの二人さえ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.50,0:02:14.84,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,気付かず通り過ぎて行く
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.51,0:02:22.46,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壊しあって　解り合ったことも
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.64,0:02:24.27,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,置き去りにした
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.39,0:02:27.71,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,これが成れの果てなの？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.84,0:02:32.25,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認めないで　立ち向かったときも
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.86,0:02:38.46,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,落ちて行く時のイメージから逃げ出せずに
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.60,0:02:43.20,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ah　何度でも探し出すよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.30,0:02:49.95,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君の目　その手の温もりを
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.17,0:02:55.29,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛はいつも私を傷つけるだけ…って君はつぶやいて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.40,0:02:59.95,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信じる事が怖くて泣いたんだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.14,0:03:02.20,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弱さを知って強くなれ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.35,0:03:05.96,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐れず信じることで
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.08,0:03:10.98,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本当の愛を知るだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.10,0:01:49.65,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}爱太过沉重而拒绝理解
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.82,0:01:54.45,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}由爱生恨之前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.59,0:01:56.42,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}任何事都是如此吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.54,0:02:01.44,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}尴尬的事由总被掩盖
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.55,0:02:04.27,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}这伪善者的真实
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.38,0:02:06.60,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}在扭曲的泥沼时代
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.75,0:02:10.36,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}本已约定的我们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.50,0:02:14.84,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}也不觉擦肩而过
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.51,0:02:22.46,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}彼此伤害
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.64,0:02:24.27,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}抛开原有的理解
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.39,0:02:27.71,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}莫非这就是末路
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.84,0:02:32.25,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}不认同命运 奋起反抗之时
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.86,0:02:38.46,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}也无法逃离坠落时的幻影
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.60,0:02:43.20,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}Ah 多少次我都能寻到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.30,0:02:49.95,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}你的瞳眸 温暖的手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.17,0:02:53.39,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}「爱永远只能给我伤害」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.49,0:02:55.29,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}你喃喃自语
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.40,0:02:59.95,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}是否曾因害怕相信而哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.14,0:03:02.20,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}承认脆弱 变得坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.35,0:03:05.96,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}不再畏惧 努力相信
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.08,0:03:10.98,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}定能找到真爱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.01,0:00:03.91,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}{\pos(350,367)}14年前 UNION领地 国际大学
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.85,0:00:06.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看过你的毕业论文了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.49,0:00:11.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无人机战斗中的战术理论与推测受损规模
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.53,0:00:15.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕业后你还是打算当战术预报员吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.80,0:00:16.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这个打算
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.20,0:00:18.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.39,0:00:23.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要留在学院 和艾弗曼教授继续研究MS
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.52,0:00:26.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说你还真厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.78,0:00:30.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年仅17岁就能毕业了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.96,0:00:32.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还差得远呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.31,0:00:35.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和卡蒂相比远未够班
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.30,0:00:38.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡蒂…战术预报的天才
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.27,0:00:43.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陆续发表的战术 在7场纷争中取得了胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.82,0:00:47.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还听说AEU正以校官待遇挖她的角
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.55,0:00:48.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是我的目标
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.18,0:00:53.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若无法阻止战争 就用战术努力尽快解决
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.66,0:00:56.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将损害抑制在最小程度 救人性命
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.79,0:01:01.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想成为卡蒂那样的战术预报员
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.42,0:01:03.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定能行的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.73,0:01:06.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕业以后就见不着了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.48,0:01:08.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真寂寞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.41,0:01:13.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可不是对小你5岁的小姑娘说的话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.35,0:01:16.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.92,0:01:19.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丽莎 毕业论文我看过了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.63,0:01:21.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真精彩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.31,0:01:22.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 卡蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.99,0:01:25.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次再见时会是在战场上吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.75,0:01:28.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望不要成为敌人就好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.65,0:01:31.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛内金…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.21,0:01:39.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你会在A-LAWS
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.87,0:01:41.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.02,0:03:19.90,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,0)}{\pos(146,360)}{\3a&HC9&\4c&H000000&\1c&HFEFDFF&}天之光
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.10,0:03:32.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上校 苏伊尔有何动静
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.90,0:03:34.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前没有变化
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.06,0:03:37.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 总会有行动的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.49,0:03:42.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反对中东重组计划的苏伊尔国力不容小觑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.27,0:03:45.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若苏伊尔开始行动
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.47,0:03:47.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他国家必然会追随
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.23,0:03:49.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了阻止这种事态
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.43,0:03:53.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联邦政府决定派遣独立治安维持部队
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.36,0:03:54.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,派遣A-LAWS?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.99,0:03:59.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联邦军已派部队驻留苏伊尔国境线了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.59,0:04:02.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以视为对苏伊尔的牵制吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.93,0:04:07.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个国王也不怕跟联邦挑起事端吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.74,0:04:10.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算有世界第一的信息产业
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.30,0:04:13.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中东全土的通信网被封锁了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.12,0:04:16.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信息也不能成为武器了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.29,0:04:23.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中东的现状 由于联邦的情报操作 对世界更为封闭了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.32,0:04:25.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苏伊尔的军事力量呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.03,0:04:26.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,详情并不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.06,0:04:29.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎拥有中东第一的军备
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.90,0:04:31.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联邦设立以前
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.44,0:04:35.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠稀有金属和信息产业成了中东第一富国嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.26,0:04:36.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太鲁莽了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.76,0:04:39.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此也不可能胜过联邦的军事力量
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.03,0:04:41.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.62,0:04:47.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是苏伊尔 也不可能在这4年间开发出超越联邦的新兵器
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.07,0:04:50.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 即使我们出动部队 也是杯水车薪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.81,0:04:53.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有一个办法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.39,0:04:56.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将苏伊尔所持有的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.73,0:04:59.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即联邦在中东的恶政
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.41,0:05:02.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通过我们KATARON的网络向全世界发送
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.07,0:05:04.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若受到舆论反对
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.63,0:05:07.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联邦也无法对中东轻举妄动了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.54,0:05:08.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.62,0:05:11.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说来 需要和苏伊尔进行交涉了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.77,0:05:14.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,池田 能和王室联系上吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.95,0:05:18.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通过当记者时代的朋友的话 应该有办法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.65,0:05:19.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.54,0:05:22.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了中东…不 为了世界
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.81,0:05:24.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.77,0:05:36.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,席琳 阿撒迪斯坦情况如何
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.62,0:05:38.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,国民们怎样了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.25,0:05:40.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,临时政府建立发表以后
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.64,0:05:42.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有什么特别的报道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.77,0:05:46.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联邦进行了对自己有利的情报控制
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.49,0:05:48.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使想去看看阿撒迪斯坦的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.82,0:05:51.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,国境线也被联邦军封锁了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.94,0:05:53.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,束手无策了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.35,0:05:54.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.98,0:05:55.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛莉娜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.69,0:06:00.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要重建阿撒迪斯坦只能打倒联邦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.40,0:06:04.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要战斗 身为皇女你有这个义务
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.79,0:06:07.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 战争只能唤来战争
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.74,0:06:12.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用暴力夺回阿撒迪斯坦 大家能获得幸福吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.70,0:06:14.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你要忍气吞声吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.52,0:06:16.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的故乡被人抢走了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.62,0:06:18.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,席琳 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.71,0:06:26.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 你什么也别做就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.28,0:06:31.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要战斗 不战斗就无法夺回祖国
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.86,0:06:39.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那 现在我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.17,0:06:43.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去故乡…失去库尔吉斯的你的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.11,0:06:48.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仿佛立足之处都在消失一般的失落感
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.03,0:06:54.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱着这种心情 为何你还能战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.87,0:06:59.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据观测班的报告
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.04,0:07:04.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天人的宇宙飞船很可能往拉格朗日3去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.38,0:07:07.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,林特少校有特殊命令
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.39,0:07:10.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追击Gundam的指挥就交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.42,0:07:11.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.23,0:07:12.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,补充兵力也安排好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.92,0:07:15.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期待你为杰江中校报仇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.58,0:07:22.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九条…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.45,0:07:29.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃米利奥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.41,0:07:33.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那事件在她心中留下了芥蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.07,0:07:39.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此 才倒向宣扬根除战争的天人理念吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.27,0:07:43.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太傻了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.01,0:07:46.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只是愚蠢的梦想而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.99,0:07:49.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界上的纷争不可能消除
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.33,0:07:56.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此我们为了防止战争延长 才当上了战术预报员 不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.03,0:08:00.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上校 我为您送餐来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.81,0:08:01.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要随便进来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.88,0:08:08.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对布林下达了攻击命令?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.89,0:08:13.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会怎么应对呢 天人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.53,0:08:23.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各传感器 一切正常
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.83,0:08:26.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粒子供给 确认为规定值
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.28,0:08:29.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿撒迪斯坦…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.75,0:08:33.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的祖国…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.57,0:08:34.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛莉娜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.09,0:08:37.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿利·阿尔·萨谢斯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.74,0:08:40.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有任何改变
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.32,0:08:42.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我什么也…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.54,0:08:45.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,E传感器有反应
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.81,0:08:47.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有机影接近中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.02,0:08:49.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人? A-LAWS吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.98,0:08:51.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.01,0:08:53.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.37,0:08:55.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.53,0:08:58.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了 危险的…东西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.06,0:09:02.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险的…东西?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.74,0:09:05.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接近中的机体速度为78千秒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.24,0:09:07.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这什么速度啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.32,0:09:10.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人只有一架?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.17,0:09:13.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Arios和Seravee还在修理中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.20,0:09:16.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam紧急出动 迎击敌机
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.22,0:09:18.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,00 先行出动
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.61,0:09:32.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.97,0:09:36.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拟太阳炉搭载型
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.67,0:09:44.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是A-LAWS
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.52,0:09:48.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这机动性 又是新型机吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.29,0:09:56.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.51,0:09:57.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN Field?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.94,0:09:59.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联邦有能用Field的机体
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.55,0:10:16.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是能用TRANS-AM
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.37,0:10:19.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.95,0:10:25.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那架新型机 压倒了00
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.33,0:10:30.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.05,0:10:34.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃了?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.22,0:10:36.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌机撤退了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.17,0:10:38.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太蹊跷了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.33,0:10:42.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收容Gundam后 最大幅度加速前往拉格朗日3
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.00,0:10:43.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.39,0:10:46.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.90,0:10:49.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告知我们他们的军队已经摆好了阵型
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.66,0:10:51.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫不保留地展示新型机性能
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.83,0:10:54.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是牵制和警告
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.51,0:10:57.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越来越需要0-Raiser了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.53,0:10:58.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.96,0:11:01.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是玛内金的佯攻?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.34,0:11:07.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会错 那架新型机的机师是变革者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.55,0:11:10.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掌握Veda的他做得到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.65,0:11:14.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也能开发出使用GN Field的机体
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.62,0:11:16.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.74,0:11:17.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提耶利亚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.90,0:11:19.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.38,0:11:21.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.75,0:11:23.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不说出他的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.95,0:11:27.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在迷惑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.49,0:11:32.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,林特少校 情况如何
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.41,0:11:36.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按计划 顺利进行中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.86,0:11:39.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情况整理好后就报告
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.22,0:11:41.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我直接指挥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.68,0:11:42.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.85,0:11:45.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.96,0:11:48.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和统一政府作对的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.28,0:11:52.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们将要承受的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.52,0:11:54.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是天雷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.94,0:11:56.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是神罚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,=========================
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.52,0:12:11.93,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(365,367)}拉格朗日3  资源卫星群
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.60,0:12:13.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闸门打开
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.32,0:12:20.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,激光探测仪与托勒密同步
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.96,0:12:31.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托勒密着陆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.69,0:12:33.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3 2 1
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.96,0:12:36.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接舷完成
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.21,0:12:38.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,固定用机械臂开始连接
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.43,0:12:42.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,登机闸开始连接
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.61,0:12:50.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟 等你们好久了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.11,0:12:54.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.26,0:12:57.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米蕾娜 还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.09,0:12:58.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.55,0:13:00.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才她说妈妈?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.54,0:13:01.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 说了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.85,0:13:02.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.03,0:13:06.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 有人还是第一次见面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.25,0:13:07.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我妻子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.61,0:13:09.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琳达·巴斯汀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.26,0:13:09.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好年轻
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.99,0:13:11.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是犯罪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.56,0:13:12.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.73,0:13:14.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩笑到此为止
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.40,0:13:15.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁说是玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.16,0:13:19.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能否尽快完成托勒密和Gundam的补给改造工作?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.25,0:13:21.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.23,0:13:23.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A-LAWS正在这片宙域部署
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.94,0:13:28.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里的隐蔽工作理应很完美啊 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.45,0:13:32.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,补给和维护最短需要五天时间
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.69,0:13:33.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.61,0:13:34.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生面孔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.98,0:13:38.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次见面 重新开始活动的同时
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.03,0:13:41.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被天人组织挖来的艾纽·雷特纳尔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.38,0:13:42.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挖来?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.34,0:13:43.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.53,0:13:45.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王留美介绍的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.01,0:13:47.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾纽可了不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.56,0:13:51.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙物理学 MS工程学 再生治疗的权威
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.70,0:13:55.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擅长驾船技术和料理 而且还是大美人儿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.85,0:13:58.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样 奇才吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.31,0:14:00.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.67,0:14:10.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,池田发来的密电
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.37,0:14:12.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说苏伊尔王室同意会谈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.44,0:14:14.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 干得好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.57,0:14:17.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会谈由我去 这里的指挥交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.13,0:14:19.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.37,0:14:21.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为防万一请带人护卫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.84,0:14:23.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 会的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.51,0:14:26.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是红轿车
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.36,0:14:27.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.82,0:14:28.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.17,0:14:31.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苏伊尔被盯上了是真的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.36,0:14:35.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别给公主殿下添麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.24,0:14:40.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 这孩子苏伊尔出身 所以很不安
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.07,0:14:46.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家为什么不能要好些呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.63,0:14:49.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 我也这么想
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.72,0:14:53.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以必须想出让大家和睦相处的办法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.40,0:14:55.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起吃饭就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.20,0:14:58.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个好主意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.52,0:14:59.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.83,0:15:03.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除此之外 还想做什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.90,0:15:09.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起玩 一起唱歌
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.24,0:15:10.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.13,0:15:12.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼此展示各自的宝贝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.40,0:15:14.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有…还有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.02,0:15:17.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.73,0:15:26.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是0-Raiser
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.13,0:15:31.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这台机体上搭载有Twin Drive的控制机能
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.80,0:15:33.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有TRANS-AM的增幅机能
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.80,0:15:34.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边的机体呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.66,0:15:38.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Arios用的支援机 GN Archer
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.66,0:15:38.41,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（GN Archer：GNR-010A）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.90,0:15:41.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN Archer…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.42,0:15:44.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始测试吧 刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.80,0:15:45.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.72,0:15:50.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉格朗日3竟然有如此大规模的基地
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.04,0:15:57.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.40,0:16:01.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.04,0:16:05.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我的错 许多人丧命
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.37,0:16:07.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须做些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.34,0:16:13.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是战斗也好 杀人也好 对我来说太…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.75,0:16:15.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做不到是很正常的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.86,0:16:22.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 必须做些什么 力所能及的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.42,0:16:26.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能冒昧问一句吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.64,0:16:27.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.90,0:16:31.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你今后也打算和他们在一起吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.36,0:16:33.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 只要阿勒路亚在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.55,0:16:36.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便被卷入战斗?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.33,0:16:41.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也曾是军人 这种觉悟早就有了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.29,0:16:48.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且已经下定决心了\N不管发生什么事我都会留在阿勒路亚身边
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.77,0:16:51.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好让人羡慕
